edu.cnm.deepdive.abq_film_tour_backend.controller

Class FilmLocationController

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.cnm.deepdive.abq_film_tour_backend.controller.FilmLocationController

  • @RestController
 @ExposesResourceFor(value=FilmLocation.class)
 @RequestMapping(value="/film_locations")
public class FilmLocationController
extends Object
    The controller for the FilmLocation entity, which also includes functionality for userComments and Images associated with the entity. Requires an associated GoogleUser.

        @PostMapping(consumes="application/json",
             produces="application/json")
public org.springframework.http.ResponseEntity<FilmLocation> post(@RequestBody
                                                                                                                                                      FilmLocation filmLocation)
        Posts a new FilmLocation. Will connect a production to the FilmLocation if a production ID is provided. Should include a site name and long and lat coordinates. Should include a Google ID, name, profile image URL for the submitter.
        Parameters:
        filmLocation - the film location
        Returns:
        the response entity
